srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dead-company-vampire-weekend-mick-fleetwood@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dead-company-vampire-weekend-mick-fleetwood@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dead-company-vampire-weekend-mick-fleetwood@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dead-company-vampire-weekend-mick-fleetwood@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dead-company-vampire-weekend-mick-fleetwood@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dead-company-vampire-weekend-mick-fleetwood@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今年 MusiCares Gala 上向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grateful-dead">感恩而死乐队</a>致敬的表演阵容已经揭晓——请查看下文。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/new-anticipated-album-releases-2025-3826243">NME 2025 年最受期待的专辑发行</a></strong></li></ul><p>本月晚些时候（1 月 31 日），Grateful Dead 将被庆祝并被评为 MusiCares 2025 年度人物。为了纪念这支传奇乐队，我们聚集了全明星阵容来表演以示敬意。据<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/music-news/musicares-grateful-dead-tribute-lineup-revealed-noah-kahan-maren-morris-billy-strings-1236112555/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》</em></a>报道，参加演出的乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-mayer">约翰·梅尔 (John Mayer)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-fleetwood">米克·弗利特伍德</a>(Mick Fleetwood) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stewart-copeland">斯图尔特·科普兰 (Stewart Copeland)</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dead-company">Dead &amp; Company</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vampire-weekend">吸血鬼周末 (Vampire Weekend)</a> 、诺亚·卡汉 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">Noah Kahan)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/norah-jones">诺拉·琼斯 (Norah Jones)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maren-morris">马伦·莫里斯 (Maren Morris)</a>等。</p><p>即将演出的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sammy-hagar">Sammy Hagar</a> 、The War On Drugs、Billy Strings、the War and Treats、Sierra Farrell 和 Lukas Nelson、My Morning Jacket 和 Dwight Yoakam。布鲁斯·霍恩斯比 (Bruce Hornsby) 预计也会出席，而安迪·科恩 (Andy Cohen) 将担任晚会的司仪。</p><p> <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/noah-kahan-billy-strings-maren-morris-grateful-dead-musicares-gala-lineup-1235241869/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》杂志</em></a>补充说，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zac-brown-band">扎克·布朗</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-matthews">戴夫·马修斯</a>和威诺娜·贾德也将演出，官方消息将很快发布。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBePpQ7OPEK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,3